title: Watch: FIESTAR’s Cao Lu, GFRIEND’s Yerin, And Rapper Kisum Reveal Teaser For Spring Collab
text:
Pin   
FIESTAR’s Cao Lu, GFRIEND’s Yerin, and rapper Kisum look lovely in the newly released teasers for their collaboration track “Spring Again.” 
The girls are dressed adorably in the pastel-toned teaser, and interestingly, they seem to be feeling both happy and bitter about the fact that spring is back. While Cao Lu and Yerin are enjoying the pretty view as flower petals fall from the sky, Kisum seems to be suffering with hay fever. 
Check out the cute teaser below!
